  N4 --> N5[UI: UI Screen (dashboard) + CWB Lifecycle snapshot / Action Item - Surface results and provide operational rollback/exception handling]
  N5 --> Z1[Outcome: Precise SKU-location demand blocs driving optimized, touchless allocations that prioritize revenue and service while respecting capacity; downstream ERP/planning/WMS/TMS updated automatically; exceptions routed for review; rapid rollback available to revert allocations if needed.]
  N3 -->|Data quality failures detected (missi...| B1[Process Builder invokes Data Quality & Validation (STREAMS) and creates Action Item/CWB for human review; pause allocation writebacks and optionally run conservative fallback allocations]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Allocation deferred until data reconciled or conservative allocations applied to protect service levels]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Computed allocations exceed productio...| B2[Process Builder calls Kinaxis RapidResponse via Remote Functions to re-optimize allocations by revenue priority; if re-optimization fails, flag for manual intervention via Action Item]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Rebalanced allocation that respects capacity or escalation to planners for exceptions]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Rollback requested within retention w...| B3[Process Builder executes Rollback Transaction node to revert writes in S4/Kinaxis and notify downstream systems; surface rollback audit in UI]
